{"title":"新北邙行（四首）","authors":["戈壁舟"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新北邙行（四首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戈壁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新北邙行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍读古人吊北邙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都叹人生是无常。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我上北邙山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里见凄凉？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见残碑荒坟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见青青麦秧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见枯柏老松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见座座新房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡鸣犬吠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前村后庄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹅游鸭戏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河池塘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首阳山前起新林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金谷园中水库汪洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望古洛城遗迹何在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见树海云水苍苍茫茫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧死新生，生生不息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日晚霞，明朝朝阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"12月11日南昌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*邙［máng］　吠［fèi］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装配车间所见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一拖拉机厂为阿尔巴尼亚装配拖拉机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装配车间里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器在轰鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人在紧张地工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又显得那样安静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个面孔严肃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那样的认真；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对对眼睛闪光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那样的兴奋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成排的拖拉机在欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向数万里的航程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问载的是什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满载着中国人民的友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕远隔重洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这车间里也能看得清："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在马克思主义旗帜下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那样的靠近。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1月30日锦江岸侧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北邙远眺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立在上清宫前望龙门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想望见周城汉城和唐城；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九代京都早已埋地下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只望见清流红瓦绿树烟云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈什么汉城宽广，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸什么壮丽的唐城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这新洛阳市里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧洛阳哪里去寻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞里伊水似凤舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云中洛河如龙腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看茫茫绿树大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排排烟囱森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"座座工厂似战舰成队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成队的战舰呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始了万里航程！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"12月20日井冈山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠某同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔别延水滨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今聚洛河侧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数日形影随，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话长从何说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同醉龙门酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相忆桥山月："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土窑共安身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山头同学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开荒一把锄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢歌一个拍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看君屋前地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲手种瓜麦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食少事且繁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥锄权当息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾饮延河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年英雄色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何畏苍松老，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼林与天接。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥手各西东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫嗟轻离别，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江河汇大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云山岂能隔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"12月20日井冈山"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}